data.description: This charming ranch is the perfect place to plant roots! Easy, one-level living with an eat-in kitchen that opens to the living room creating a nice, open area for entertaining friends & family. Down the hall, you will find 3 generously sized bedrooms as well as a full bathroom. Many big ticket items are recent including a new oil tank, an approximately 9-year-old well, septic, and electric panel. Spacious backyard offers plenty of space to enjoy your favorite outdoor activities. Convenient location near many amenities. Perfect for a 1st-time buyer or someone looking to simplify and downsize. Come check out all this home has to offer!
